This project presents an end-to-end Power BI dashboard built using real hotel data from Booking and Expedia platforms.

The goal is to analyze:
- Operational performance
- Channel efficiency
- Guest segmentation
- Review trends and reputation

## ğŸ§± Data Sources
- Booking.com (Check-ins, cancellations, reviews since 2022)
- Expedia (Check-ins, cancellations, reviews since 2024)

All data has been anonymized.

## ğŸ“Š KPIs
- Total Check-ins
- Cancellation Rate
